templates/NOTES.txt
---
1. Get the application URL by running these commands if ingress is enabled:

  export POD_NAME=$(kubectl get pods -l app={{ .Values.appName }} -n {{ .Values.namespace | default .Release.Namespace }} -o jsonpath="{.items[0].metadata.name}")
  kubectl port-forward $POD_NAME 8080:80 -n {{ .Values.namespace | default .Release.Namespace }}

2. To access via ingress, make sure your DNS points to your ingress controller and visit http://{{ (index .Values.ingress.hosts 0).host }}

