README.md
---
# smart-alarm-web-app-fe Helm Chart

This Helm chart deploys the Smart Alarm frontend ({{ .Values.appName }}) into a Kubernetes cluster (k3s compatible).

## Features
- Deployment with configurable replica count and resources
- ClusterIP Service
- Optional Ingress
- ImagePullSecrets support
- Readiness & Liveness probes

## Usage
Install:

```bash
helm install smart-alarm ./smart-alarm-web-app-fe -n smart-alarm --create-namespace
```

To enable ingress, set `ingress.enabled=true` and update hosts in `values.yaml` or with `--set`.
